{"lang": "zh_TW", "eventid": "act32side", "eventName": "水晶箭行動", "entryType": "ACTIVITY", "storyCode": "CR-ST-3", "avgTag": "幕間", "storyName": "藝術館餐廳", "storyInfo": "雷內爾被遣返，上尉被審判，社區則意外獲得了藝術館的所有權。而虹彩小隊的隊員們一邊為如何回到自己的世界頭痛，一邊思考泰拉的未來。\n", "storyList": [{"id": 0, "prop": "HEADER", "attributes": {"key": "title_test", "is_skippable": "true", "fit_mode": "BLACK_MASK"}}, {"id": 1, "prop": "stopmusic", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 2, "prop": "dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 3, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 0.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 0.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 4, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 1.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 2.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 5, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 6, "prop": "PlayMusic", "attributes": {"intro": "$darkness01_intro", "key": "$darkness01_loop", "volume": 0.6}}, {"id": 7, "prop": "Background", "attributes": {"image": "bg_cellroomB", "screenadapt": "coverall"}}, {"id": 8, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 0.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 2.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 9, "prop": "Delay", "attributes": {"time": 1.0}}, {"id": 10, "prop": "PlaySound", "attributes": {"key": "$dooropenquite", "volume": 1.0}}, {"id": 11, "prop": "delay", "attributes": {"time": 1.5}}, {"id": 12, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "r", "name": "avg_npc_1211_1#8$1", "duration": 0.5, "isblock": "true"}}, {"id": 13, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "我記得現在是午休時間，如果需要提審，你可能要晚點來——", "name": "雷內爾"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1211_1#8$1"}, {"id": 14, "prop": "dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 15, "prop": "PlaySound", "attributes": {"key": "$d_gen_walk_n", "volume": 1.0}}, {"id": 16, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "l", "name": "avg_486_espumo_1#7", "duration": 1.5, "isblock": "true"}}, {"id": 17, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "l", "focus": "l"}}, {"id": 18, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "我不是來提審你的。", "name": "龍舌蘭"}, "figure_art": "avg_486_espumo_1#7"}, {"id": 19, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "r", "name": "avg_npc_1211_1#10$1", "focus": "r"}}, {"id": 20, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "你是……", "name": "雷內爾"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1211_1#10$1"}, {"id": 21, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "哦，怎麼，羅德島也想踩著我的屍體分一杯羹嗎？歡迎歡迎。", "name": "雷內爾"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1211_1#10$1"}, {"id": 22, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "l", "name": "avg_486_espumo_1#7", "focus": "l"}}, {"id": 23, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "我只是來替坎黛拉女士告知你多索雷斯對你的最終處理結果。", "name": "龍舌蘭"}, "figure_art": "avg_486_espumo_1#7"}, {"id": 24, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "依據多索雷斯市長辦公室的判斷，多索雷斯將不會審判你的罪行。", "name": "龍舌蘭"}, "figure_art": "avg_486_espumo_1#7"}, {"id": 25, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "r", "name": "avg_npc_1211_1#10$1", "focus": "r"}}, {"id": 26, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "讓我猜猜，把我交給聯合政府？", "name": "雷內爾"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1211_1#10$1"}, {"id": 27, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "雖然馬特奧是個蠢貨，但他畢竟是聯合政府在多索雷斯的代表。", "name": "雷內爾"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1211_1#10$1"}, {"id": 28, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "r", "name": "avg_npc_1211_1#9$1", "focus": "r"}}, {"id": 29, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "嗯……我三番五次地耍他玩，聯合政府肯定等不及要把我挫骨揚灰。", "name": "雷內爾"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1211_1#9$1"}, {"id": 30, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "l", "name": "avg_486_espumo_1#7", "focus": "l"}}, {"id": 31, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "你對局勢的判斷很精準。聯合政府確實想把你抓去拉烏尼達公審，就像他們對馬特奧做的一樣。", "name": "龍舌蘭"}, "figure_art": "avg_486_espumo_1#7"}, {"id": 32, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "r", "name": "avg_npc_1211_1#2$1", "focus": "r"}}, {"id": 33, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "一場公審？很好，我很期待。", "name": "雷內爾"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1211_1#2$1"}, {"id": 34, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "l", "name": "avg_486_espumo_1#1", "focus": "l"}}, {"id": 35, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "不，雷內爾先生。", "name": "龍舌蘭"}, "figure_art": "avg_486_espumo_1#1"}, {"id": 36, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "你將被送回卡西米爾。", "name": "龍舌蘭"}, "figure_art": "avg_486_espumo_1#1"}, {"id": 37, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "r", "name": "avg_npc_1211_1#5$1", "focus": "r"}}, {"id": 38, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "……你再說一次？", "name": "雷內爾"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1211_1#5$1"}, {"id": 39, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "l", "name": "avg_486_espumo_1#1", "focus": "l"}}, {"id": 40, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "商業聯合會向坎黛拉施加了壓力，希望將你送回卡西米爾。", "name": "龍舌蘭"}, "figure_art": "avg_486_espumo_1#1"}, {"id": 41, "prop": "CameraShake", "attributes": {"duration": 0.3, "xstrength": 30.0, "ystrength": 30.0, "vibrato": 30.0, "randomness": 90.0, "fadeout": "true", "block": "false"}}, {"id": 42, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "r", "name": "avg_npc_1211_1#4$1", "focus": "r"}}, {"id": 43, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "你再說一次？！", "name": "雷內爾"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1211_1#4$1"}, {"id": 44, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "l", "name": "avg_486_espumo_1#1", "focus": "l"}}, {"id": 45, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "你父親在聯合會中留下的人脈發揮了作用，你現在不必留在多索雷斯，也不用去拉烏尼達，你可以回家了。", "name": "龍舌蘭"}, "figure_art": "avg_486_espumo_1#1"}, {"id": 46, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "r", "name": "avg_npc_1211_1#7$1", "focus": "r"}}, {"id": 47, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "不……我不會回去。", "name": "雷內爾"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1211_1#7$1"}, {"id": 48, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "我不會回到那些最卑鄙、最下賤、最可悲的東西中去……", "name": "雷內爾"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1211_1#7$1"}, {"id": 49, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "l", "name": "avg_486_espumo_1#7", "focus": "l"}}, {"id": 50, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "事到如今也由不得你了，雷內爾先生，不管你的最終歸屬是哪裡，都是你魯莽行動造成的結果。", "name": "龍舌蘭"}, "figure_art": "avg_486_espumo_1#7"}, {"id": 51, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "是苦是甜，你都得自己嚥下。", "name": "龍舌蘭"}, "figure_art": "avg_486_espumo_1#7"}, {"id": 52, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "r", "name": "avg_npc_1211_1#8$1", "focus": "r"}}, {"id": 53, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "呵，老東西……你還真是陰魂不散啊。", "name": "雷內爾"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1211_1#8$1"}, {"id": 54, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "l", "name": "avg_486_espumo_1#3", "focus": "l"}}, {"id": 55, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "對了，還有一件事，你需要決定你財產的歸屬問題。", "name": "龍舌蘭"}, "figure_art": "avg_486_espumo_1#3"}, {"id": 56, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "r", "name": "avg_npc_1211_1#8$1", "focus": "r"}}, {"id": 57, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "說得好像，我真的能自己決定一樣，坎黛拉不是早就想方設法把它們挪去其他地方了嗎？", "name": "雷內爾"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1211_1#8$1"}, {"id": 58, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "l", "name": "avg_486_espumo_1#2", "focus": "l"}}, {"id": 59, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "還有一些固定資產……沒有人敢接手……", "name": "龍舌蘭"}, "figure_art": "avg_486_espumo_1#2"}, {"id": 60, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "你就在這份轉讓合約上隨便寫個名字吧。", "name": "龍舌蘭"}, "figure_art": "avg_486_espumo_1#2"}, {"id": 61, "prop": "dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 62, "prop": "playsound", "attributes": {"key": "$d_avg_paper1", "volume": 1.0}}, {"id": 63, "prop": "delay", "attributes": {"time": 0.5}}, {"id": 64, "prop": "playsound", "attributes": {"key": "$d_avg_paper2", "volume": 1.0}}, {"id": 65, "prop": "delay", "attributes": {"time": 1.0}}, {"id": 66, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "r", "name": "avg_npc_1211_1#10$1", "focus": "r"}}, {"id": 67, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "……那就是下一個路過這裡的人好了——", "name": "雷內爾"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1211_1#10$1"}, {"id": 68, "prop": "dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 69, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 70, "prop": "PlaySound", "attributes": {"key": "$d_gen_walk_n", "volume": 1.0}}, {"id": 71, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_1214_1#1$1", "duration": 1.5, "isblock": "true"}}, {"id": 72, "prop": "delay", "attributes": {"time": 0.5}}, {"id": 73, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_486_espumo_1#3"}}, {"id": 74, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "迪亞茲先生，你來監區幹什麼？？", "name": "龍舌蘭"}, "figure_art": "avg_486_espumo_1#3"}, {"id": 75, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_1214_1#10$1"}}, {"id": 76, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "指認假裝人質的馬特奧手下啊。反倒是你，你叫我幹嘛？", "name": "迪亞茲"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1214_1#10$1"}, {"id": 77, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_486_espumo_1#4"}}, {"id": 78, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "沒、沒事。", "name": "龍舌蘭"}, "figure_art": "avg_486_espumo_1#4"}, {"id": 79, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_1214_1#1$1"}}, {"id": 80, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "那我走了。", "name": "迪亞茲"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1214_1#1$1"}, {"id": 81, "prop": "dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 82, "prop": "PlaySound", "attributes": {"key": "$d_gen_walk_n", "volume": 1.0}}, {"id": 83, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"duration": 1.5, "isblock": "true"}}, {"id": 84, "prop": "delay", "attributes": {"time": 0.5}}, {"id": 85, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "r", "name": "avg_npc_1211_1#1$1", "focus": "n"}}, {"id": 86, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "l", "name": "avg_486_espumo_1#4", "focus": "l"}}, {"id": 87, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "欸……你……反正還沒落筆，你隨時可以反悔——", "name": "龍舌蘭"}, "figure_art": "avg_486_espumo_1#4"}, {"id": 88, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "r", "name": "avg_npc_1211_1#1$1", "focus": "r"}}, {"id": 89, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "反悔？我從來都不反悔。", "name": "雷內爾"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1211_1#1$1"}, {"id": 90, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "……何況，這麼一想也不賴。", "name": "雷內爾"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1211_1#1$1"}, {"id": 91, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "把它留給真正熱愛藝術的傢伙。", "name": "雷內爾"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1211_1#1$1"}, {"id": 92, "prop": "dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 93, "prop": "PlaySound", "attributes": {"key": "$d_avg_penrustle", "volume": 1.0}}, {"id": 94, "prop": "delay", "attributes": {"time": 1.0}}, {"id": 95, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 0.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 0.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 96, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 1.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 2.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 97, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 98, "prop": "Background", "attributes": {"image": "bg_20_G01", "screenadapt": "coverall"}}, {"id": 99, "prop": "Delay", "attributes": {"time": 1.0}}, {"id": 100, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "l", "name": "avg_486_espumo_1#1"}}, {"id": 101, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "r", "name": "avg_npc_198_1#1"}}, {"id": 102, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 0.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 2.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 103, "prop": "Delay", "attributes": {"time": 1.0}}, {"id": 104, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "r", "name": "avg_npc_198_1#1", "focus": "r"}}, {"id": 105, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "雷內爾最後真的把那位老消防員的名字寫上去了？", "name": "坎黛拉"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_198_1#1"}, {"id": 106, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "l", "name": "avg_486_espumo_1#1", "focus": "l"}}, {"id": 107, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "是的。送他出多索雷斯的時候，我最後向他確認了一次，他還是在監區的那套說辭。", "name": "龍舌蘭"}, "figure_art": "avg_486_espumo_1#1"}, {"id": 108, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "r", "name": "avg_npc_198_1#1", "focus": "r"}}, {"id": 109, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "……他真是連他父親一丁點的特質都沒有繼承。", "name": "坎黛拉"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_198_1#1"}, {"id": 110, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "l", "name": "avg_486_espumo_1#1", "focus": "l"}}, {"id": 111, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "說實話，他大概不討厭這種評價。", "name": "龍舌蘭"}, "figure_art": "avg_486_espumo_1#1"}, {"id": 112, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "r", "name": "avg_npc_198_1#1", "focus": "r"}}, {"id": 113, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "當然，但這句話可不是在誇他。", "name": "坎黛拉"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_198_1#1"}, {"id": 114, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "l", "name": "avg_486_espumo_1#6", "focus": "l"}}, {"id": 115, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "哈哈……", "name": "龍舌蘭"}, "figure_art": "avg_486_espumo_1#6"}, {"id": 116, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 117, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "focus": "n"}}, {"id": 118, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "坎黛拉女士，您和埃內斯托先生的咖啡。", "name": "市長保鏢"}}, {"id": 119, "prop": "dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 120, "prop": "PlaySound", "attributes": {"key": "$d_avg_plateplace", "volume": 1.0}}, {"id": 121, "prop": "delay", "attributes": {"time": 1.5}}, {"id": 122, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "r", "name": "avg_npc_198_1#1", "focus": "n"}}, {"id": 123, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "l", "name": "avg_486_espumo_1#3", "focus": "l"}}, {"id": 124, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "好濃的香氣！布克先生，我能請教一下用的是哪種咖啡豆嗎？", "name": "龍舌蘭"}, "figure_art": "avg_486_espumo_1#3"}, {"id": 125, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "focus": "n"}}, {"id": 126, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "是坎黛拉女士最近常喝的三種深烘豆拼配。請二位慢用。", "name": "市長保鏢"}}, {"id": 127, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "r", "name": "avg_npc_198_1#4", "focus": "r"}}, {"id": 128, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "現在事情告一段落，要見見你在多索雷斯其他的熟人嗎？", "name": "坎黛拉"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_198_1#4"}, {"id": 129, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "l", "name": "avg_486_espumo_1#1", "focus": "l"}}, {"id": 130, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "其實我在進城之前沒想過要驚動任何人。", "name": "龍舌蘭"}, "figure_art": "avg_486_espumo_1#1"}, {"id": 131, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "r", "name": "avg_npc_198_1#2", "focus": "r"}}, {"id": 132, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "的確，如果一切都風平浪靜的話，你本可以不驚動任何人，但多索雷斯永遠不可能風平浪靜，你從來都知道這一點。", "name": "坎黛拉"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_198_1#2"}, {"id": 133, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "l", "name": "avg_486_espumo_1#1", "focus": "l"}}, {"id": 134, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "……是啊。", "name": "龍舌蘭"}, "figure_art": "avg_486_espumo_1#1"}, {"id": 135, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "r", "name": "avg_npc_198_1#1", "focus": "r"}}, {"id": 136, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "就像現在，雷內爾的這場鬧劇過後，聯合政府在多索雷斯的聲勢遭到了沉重打擊。", "name": "坎黛拉"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_198_1#1"}, {"id": 137, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "儘管從拉烏尼達寄來的抗議信一封接一封，但雷內爾和他的財產，他們想都別想。多索雷斯不是他們俯首貼耳的附庸。", "name": "坎黛拉"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_198_1#1"}, {"id": 138, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "可與之相應，其餘雙方也已經迫不及待——", "name": "坎黛拉"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_198_1#1"}, {"id": 139, "prop": "dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 140, "prop": "delay", "attributes": {"time": 1.0}}, {"id": 141, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "r", "name": "avg_npc_198_1#4", "focus": "r"}}, {"id": 142, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "……看看我，光顧著說這些沒意思的東西了。", "name": "坎黛拉"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_198_1#4"}, {"id": 143, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "l", "name": "avg_486_espumo_1#1", "focus": "l"}}, {"id": 144, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "怎麼會，這些都是很有意義的訊息。", "name": "龍舌蘭"}, "figure_art": "avg_486_espumo_1#1"}, {"id": 145, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "r", "name": "avg_npc_198_1#3", "focus": "r"}}, {"id": 146, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "來，埃內斯托，嚐嚐看這種拼配合不合你的口味。", "name": "坎黛拉"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_198_1#3"}, {"id": 147, "prop": "dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 148, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "l", "focus": "l"}}, {"id": 149, "prop": "PlaySound", "attributes": {"key": "$d_avg_drinkswllw", "volume": 1.0}}, {"id": 150, "prop": "delay", "attributes": {"time": 1.5}}, {"id": 151, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "l", "name": "avg_486_espumo_1#3", "focus": "l"}}, {"id": 152, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "很濃郁……但也很奇妙的口感。", "name": "龍舌蘭"}, "figure_art": "avg_486_espumo_1#3"}, {"id": 153, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "r", "name": "avg_npc_198_1#5", "focus": "r"}}, {"id": 154, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "說來聽聽？", "name": "坎黛拉"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_198_1#5"}, {"id": 155, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "l", "name": "avg_486_espumo_1#1", "focus": "l"}}, {"id": 156, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "我能分辨出三種豆的品種和香氣，但我說不清究竟哪種豆才是其中佔比最大的。", "name": "龍舌蘭"}, "figure_art": "avg_486_espumo_1#1"}, {"id": 157, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "三種香氣原本各自為戰，此消彼長，可很快又會在口中融匯成濃烈的焦香，再也不分彼此。", "name": "龍舌蘭"}, "figure_art": "avg_486_espumo_1#1"}, {"id": 158, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "r", "name": "avg_npc_198_1#1", "focus": "r"}}, {"id": 159, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "精準。", "name": "坎黛拉"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_198_1#1"}, {"id": 160, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "這種拼配最大的賣點在於它沒有嚴苛的比例限制，只要三種豆的佔比不出現太大差距，就總能保持這種穩定的焦香。", "name": "坎黛拉"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_198_1#1"}, {"id": 161, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "l", "name": "avg_486_espumo_1#2", "focus": "l"}}, {"id": 162, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "原來是這樣。", "name": "龍舌蘭"}, "figure_art": "avg_486_espumo_1#2"}, {"id": 163, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "r", "name": "avg_npc_198_1#4", "focus": "r"}}, {"id": 164, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "怎麼樣，合你的口味嗎？", "name": "坎黛拉"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_198_1#4"}, {"id": 165, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "l", "name": "avg_486_espumo_1#4", "focus": "l"}}, {"id": 166, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "我……", "name": "龍舌蘭"}, "figure_art": "avg_486_espumo_1#4"}, {"id": 167, "prop": "dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 168, "prop": "delay", "attributes": {"time": 1.5}}, {"id": 169, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "r", "name": "avg_npc_198_1#4", "focus": "r"}}, {"id": 170, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "還沒辦法下結論？", "name": "坎黛拉"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_198_1#4"}, {"id": 171, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "l", "name": "avg_486_espumo_1#2", "focus": "l"}}, {"id": 172, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "……", "name": "龍舌蘭"}, "figure_art": "avg_486_espumo_1#2"}, {"id": 173, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "r", "name": "avg_npc_198_1#1", "focus": "r"}}, {"id": 174, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "沒關係，那家店就在那裡，只要你回來，隨時都喝得到。", "name": "坎黛拉"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_198_1#1"}, {"id": 175, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "不僅如此，只要你想，讓那家咖啡店以你的想法調配豆子，甚至往咖啡裡加氣泡水，也絕非不可能。", "name": "坎黛拉"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_198_1#1"}, {"id": 176, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "l", "name": "avg_486_espumo_1#1", "focus": "l"}}, {"id": 177, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "哈哈，您說笑了。", "name": "龍舌蘭"}, "figure_art": "avg_486_espumo_1#1"}, {"id": 178, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "r", "name": "avg_npc_198_1#1", "focus": "r"}}, {"id": 179, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "說笑嗎？我倒不這麼認為。", "name": "坎黛拉"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_198_1#1"}, {"id": 180, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "因為我的確很期待你的選擇，埃內斯托。", "name": "坎黛拉"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_198_1#1"}, {"id": 181, "prop": "dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 182, "prop": "musicvolume", "attributes": {"volume": 0.2, "fadetime": 2.0}}, {"id": 183, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 0.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 0.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 184, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 1.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 2.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 185, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 186, "prop": "Background", "attributes": {"image": "bg_20_G02", "screenadapt": "coverall"}}, {"id": 187, "prop": "Delay", "attributes": {"time": 1.0}}, {"id": 188, "prop": "musicvolume", "attributes": {"volume": 0.6, "fadetime": 2.0}}, {"id": 189, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "r", "name": "avg_282_catap_1#9$1"}}, {"id": 190, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 0.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 2.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 191, "prop": "Delay", "attributes": {"time": 1.0}}, {"id": 192, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "喲，埃內斯托，你和這位坎黛拉市長聊了好長時間啊。", "name": "空爆"}, "figure_art": "avg_282_catap_1#9$1"}, {"id": 193, "prop": "dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 194, "prop": "PlaySound", "attributes": {"key": "$d_gen_walk_n", "volume": 1.0}}, {"id": 195, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "l", "name": "avg_486_espumo_1#1", "duration": 1.5, "isblock": "true"}}, {"id": 196, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "l", "focus": "l"}}, {"id": 197, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "沒辦法，我和她也算是老相識，還有蠻多東西要聊的。", "name": "龍舌蘭"}, "figure_art": "avg_486_espumo_1#1"}, {"id": 198, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "r", "name": "avg_282_catap_1#9$1", "focus": "r"}}, {"id": 199, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "聊了這麼久，她是不是還挺喜歡你的？", "name": "空爆"}, "figure_art": "avg_282_catap_1#9$1"}, {"id": 200, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "l", "name": "avg_486_espumo_1#1", "focus": "l"}}, {"id": 201, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "還好吧。", "name": "龍舌蘭"}, "figure_art": "avg_486_espumo_1#1"}, {"id": 202, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "r", "name": "avg_282_catap_1#5$1", "focus": "r"}}, {"id": 203, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "你這個人……跟自己相關的東西，是真的一句話也不願多說啊。", "name": "空爆"}, "figure_art": "avg_282_catap_1#5$1"}, {"id": 204, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "r", "name": "avg_282_catap_1#1$1", "focus": "r"}}, {"id": 205, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "算了，既然你不願意說，那我就不打聽了，哼哼……", "name": "空爆"}, "figure_art": "avg_282_catap_1#1$1"}, {"id": 206, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "l", "name": "avg_486_espumo_1#5", "focus": "l"}}, {"id": 207, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "就算你去問拉菲艾拉，她也不會告訴你的。", "name": "龍舌蘭"}, "figure_art": "avg_486_espumo_1#5"}, {"id": 208, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "r", "name": "avg_282_catap_1#5$1", "focus": "r"}}, {"id": 209, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "你是會什麼讀心的源石技藝嗎？你怎麼知道我要去問拉菲艾拉的？", "name": "空爆"}, "figure_art": "avg_282_catap_1#5$1"}, {"id": 210, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "l", "name": "avg_486_espumo_1#5", "focus": "l"}}, {"id": 211, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "都寫在你臉上了。", "name": "龍舌蘭"}, "figure_art": "avg_486_espumo_1#5"}, {"id": 212, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "r", "name": "avg_282_catap_1#7$1", "focus": "r"}}, {"id": 213, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "嘖嘖嘖，這人好可怕啊。", "name": "空爆"}, "figure_art": "avg_282_catap_1#7$1"}, {"id": 214, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "l", "name": "avg_486_espumo_1#1", "focus": "l"}}, {"id": 215, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "順便，我倒是從早上出發前就知道一定會遲到，也很感謝你一直在這裡等我，但我們現在已經錯過和迪亞茲約好的時間了哦？", "name": "龍舌蘭"}, "figure_art": "avg_486_espumo_1#1"}, {"id": 216, "prop": "stopmusic", "attributes": {"fadetime": 2.0}}, {"id": 217, "prop": "CameraShake", "attributes": {"duration": 0.3, "xstrength": 30.0, "ystrength": 30.0, "vibrato": 30.0, "randomness": 90.0, "fadeout": "true", "block": "false"}}, {"id": 218, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "r", "name": "avg_282_catap_1#5$1", "focus": "r"}}, {"id": 219, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "——糟了！", "name": "空爆"}, "figure_art": "avg_282_catap_1#5$1"}, {"id": 220, "prop": "dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 221, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 1.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 2.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 222, "prop": "background", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 223, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 224, "prop": "Background", "attributes": {"image": "bg_desert_1", "screenadapt": "coverall"}}, {"id": 225, "prop": "PlaySound", "attributes": {"key": "$d_avg_drivestop", "volume": 1.0}}, {"id": 226, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 0.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 2.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 227, "prop": "delay", "attributes": {"time": 1.0}}, {"id": 228, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "那麼，雷內爾·科瓦爾斯基先生，您請先上車，我去拿行李。", "name": "商業聯合會員工"}}, {"id": 229, "prop": "dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 230, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_1211_1#10$1"}}, {"id": 231, "prop": "delay", "attributes": {"time": 1.0}}, {"id": 232, "prop": "PlaySound", "attributes": {"key": "$d_gen_walk_n", "volume": 1.0}}, {"id": 233, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"duration": 1.5, "isblock": "true"}}, {"id": 234, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "雷內爾面無表情地坐進後座，等車門合上後，他覺得溫度有些高，於是將外套脫下放在一旁，隨後倚在靠背上，正準備鬆開自己的衣領。"}}, {"id": 235, "prop": "dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 236, "prop": "PlaySound", "attributes": {"key": "$d_avg_punch02", "volume": 0.4}}, {"id": 237, "prop": "delay", "attributes": {"time": 1.0}}, {"id": 238, "prop": "PlaySound", "attributes": {"key": "$bodyfalldown2", "volume": 0.8}}, {"id": 239, "prop": "delay", "attributes": {"time": 1.0}}, {"id": 240, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "但車外一聲異響打斷了他的動作，他轉頭看向窗外，看見商業聯合會的員工暈倒在車旁，不省人事。"}}, {"id": 241, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "隨後，輕敲玻璃的聲響從車的另一側響起，他順著聲音回頭，看見有個熟悉的人站在車外。"}}, {"id": 242, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "雷內爾搖下車窗，與一雙黑亮的眼睛對上。"}}, {"id": 243, "prop": "dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 244, "prop": "PlayMusic", "attributes": {"intro": "$newhope01_intro", "key": "$newhope01_loop", "volume": 0.6}}, {"id": 245, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_1213_1#8$1", "duration": 1.5, "isblock": "true"}}, {"id": 246, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "可以麻煩您載我一程嗎，先生？", "name": "米沃什"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1213_1#8$1"}, {"id": 247, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_1211_1#10$1"}}, {"id": 248, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "那你要去哪裡呢？", "name": "雷內爾"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1211_1#10$1"}, {"id": 249, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_1213_1#8$1"}}, {"id": 250, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "這不一向是由你來決定的嗎？", "name": "米沃什"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1213_1#8$1"}, {"id": 251, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_1211_1#2$1"}}, {"id": 252, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "以前你總跟著我四處奔波，或許這次該由你來決定我們的目的地。", "name": "雷內爾"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1211_1#2$1"}, {"id": 253, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_1211_1#10$1"}}, {"id": 254, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "你真的沒有想去的地方嗎，米沃什？", "name": "雷內爾"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1211_1#10$1"}, {"id": 255, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_1213_1#9$1"}}, {"id": 256, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "去哪裡都一樣，不是嗎？", "name": "米沃什"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1213_1#9$1"}, {"id": 257, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_1211_1#9$1"}}, {"id": 258, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "還是有些不一樣的，這次我真的身無分文了，除了後車箱那兩個行李箱。", "name": "雷內爾"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1211_1#9$1"}, {"id": 259, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_1213_1#8$1"}}, {"id": 260, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "既然如此，我來開車好了，等到燃料耗盡，車停在哪裡，我們就去哪裡。", "name": "米沃什"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1213_1#8$1"}, {"id": 261, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_1211_1#9$1"}}, {"id": 262, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "嗯……好，你說了算。", "name": "雷內爾"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1211_1#9$1"}, {"id": 263, "prop": "dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 264, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 265, "prop": "PlaySound", "attributes": {"key": "$d_avg_cardoorc", "volume": 1.0}}, {"id": 266, "prop": "curtain", "attributes": {"direction": 0.0, "fillfrom": 0.01, "fillto": 0.11, "fadetime": 1.5}}, {"id": 267, "prop": "curtain", "attributes": {"direction": 4.0, "fillfrom": 0.01, "fillto": 0.11, "fadetime": 1.5}}, {"id": 268, "prop": "delay", "attributes": {"time": 1.5}}, {"id": 269, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "衝著雷內爾露出一個笑容，米沃什打開前門，坐上了駕駛位，在啟動前，他從後視鏡看到了雷內爾的臉。"}}, {"id": 270, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "此刻，雷內爾的表情混合著迷惑、欣喜和些許的猶豫。"}}, {"id": 271, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "l", "name": "avg_npc_1213_1#7$1", "focus": "l"}}, {"id": 272, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "r", "name": "avg_npc_1211_1#10$1", "focus": "n"}}, {"id": 273, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "你看起來有些話想問我。", "name": "米沃什"}}, {"id": 274, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "r", "name": "avg_npc_1211_1#10$1", "focus": "r"}}, {"id": 275, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "為什麼回來？為什麼不離開？", "name": "雷內爾"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1211_1#10$1"}, {"id": 276, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "l", "name": "avg_npc_1213_1#1$1", "focus": "l"}}, {"id": 277, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "你難道不知道答案嗎？", "name": "米沃什"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1213_1#1$1"}, {"id": 278, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "r", "name": "avg_npc_1211_1#10$1", "focus": "r"}}, {"id": 279, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "也許我不是詢問，我只是想證實那個答案。", "name": "雷內爾"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1211_1#10$1"}, {"id": 280, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "l", "name": "avg_npc_1213_1#2$1", "focus": "l"}}, {"id": 281, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "……別這麼篤定，或許我很快就會因為忍受不了你而選擇離開。", "name": "米沃什"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1213_1#2$1"}, {"id": 282, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "r", "name": "avg_npc_1211_1#9$1", "focus": "r"}}, {"id": 283, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "但不是今天。", "name": "雷內爾"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1211_1#9$1"}, {"id": 284, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "l", "name": "avg_npc_1213_1#8$1", "focus": "l"}}, {"id": 285, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "對，不是今天。", "name": "米沃什"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1213_1#8$1"}, {"id": 286, "prop": "dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 287, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"duration": 1.0, "isblock": "true"}}, {"id": 288, "prop": "PlaySound", "attributes": {"key": "$sportscarstart", "volume": 1.0}}, {"id": 289, "prop": "delay", "attributes": {"time": 1.0}}, {"id": 290, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "從後視鏡收回視線，米沃什重重發動引擎，銀色轎車絕塵而去。"}}, {"id": 291, "prop": "dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 292, "prop": "stopmusic", "attributes": {"fadetime": 2.0}}, {"id": 293, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 0.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 0.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 294, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 1.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 2.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 295, "prop": "curtain", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 296, "prop": "background", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 297, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 298, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "如今，克里斯達爾藝術館的展廳仍然保持著那一天的樣貌。"}}, {"id": 299, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "破碎的展櫃，被燒焦的地面，出現裂痕的牆體；五彩斑斕的射燈，肆意妄為的塗鴉，狂放不羈的音樂……"}}, {"id": 300, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "除了房間正中央的大圓桌。"}}, {"id": 301, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "火候正好的烤肉正在桌上上滋滋作響，散發出誘人的香氣。"}}, {"id": 302, "prop": "dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 303, "prop": "Image", "attributes": {"image": "48_i12", "screenadapt": "coverall", "xScale": 1.05, "yScale": 1.05, "fadetime": 0.0}}, {"id": 304, "prop": "ImageTween", "attributes": {"xScaleFrom": 1.05, "yScaleFrom": 1.05, "xScaleTo": 1.0, "yScaleTo": 1.0, "duration": 20.0, "block": "false"}}, {"id": 305, "prop": "Delay", "attributes": {"time": 1.0}}, {"id": 306, "prop": "PlaySound", "attributes": {"key": "$d_avg_crwddiscuss_inside", "volume": 0.2, "loop": "true", "channel": "c"}}, {"id": 307, "prop": "PlayMusic", "attributes": {"intro": "$warm_intro", "key": "$warm_loop", "volume": 0.6}}, {"id": 308, "prop": "PlaySound", "attributes": {"key": "$d_avg_tdhbdzjczs", "volume": 0.0, "loop": "true", "channel": "s"}}, {"id": 309, "prop": "SoundVolume", "attributes": {"volume": 0.6, "channel": "s", "fadetime": 2.0}}, {"id": 310, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 0.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 2.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 311, "prop": "Delay", "attributes": {"time": 1.0}}, {"id": 312, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "動手啊，怎麼都沒反應？難道不餓？", "name": "迪亞茲"}}, {"id": 313, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "……只是沒想到這裡會變成烤肉店。", "name": "ELA"}}, {"id": 314, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "唉，這棟樓被當成了戰場，又被炸彈炸了一通，那些藝術品沒辦法放在這，樓空著又可惜，不如拿來弄點副業。", "name": "迪亞茲"}}, {"id": 315, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "剛好多索雷斯電視台缺了雷內爾這個熱點，開始把鼻子伸到我們社區來，造謠說我們的藝術家們沒人會做飯，整天吃仙人掌乾過日子。", "name": "迪亞茲"}}, {"id": 316, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "我倒要讓他們看看什麼才是真正的玻利瓦爾美食！", "name": "迪亞茲"}}, {"id": 317, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "那，這個串烤洋蔥蘑菇馱獸肉來一份——", "name": "FUZE"}}, {"id": 318, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "兩份。", "name": "TACHANKA"}}, {"id": 319, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "沒問題！", "name": "迪亞茲"}}, {"id": 320, "prop": "SoundVolume", "attributes": {"volume": 0.2, "channel": "s", "fadetime": 2.0}}, {"id": 321, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "呼……迪亞茲先生的手藝真是沒話說啊。", "name": "ASH"}}, {"id": 322, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "說真的，我們四個也在泰拉遊歷了許多地方，玻利瓦爾的烤肉可還是第一次品嚐。", "name": "BLITZ"}}, {"id": 323, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "你們之前都去了哪裡？", "name": "IANA"}}, {"id": 324, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "我們一開始落在了薩爾貢的荒漠裡，在羅德島短暫停留，取得了“虹彩小隊”身分之後，我們各自又去了一些地方。", "name": "BLITZ"}}, {"id": 325, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "薩爾貢的雨林，薩米的冰原，哥倫比亞的礦場和城市，烏薩斯針葉林間的村莊……", "name": "BLITZ"}}, {"id": 326, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "儘管如此，我們踏足過的地方也只是這片大地很小的一部分。", "name": "FROST"}}, {"id": 327, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "唯一的遺憾是列維·克里奇科和他瘋狂的實驗室一起埋在了薩爾貢的地下。", "name": "TACHANKA"}}, {"id": 328, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "如果有人犯了思鄉病，恐怕只能找一條跟來時不一樣的路回去了。", "name": "TACHANKA"}}, {"id": 329, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "那你們找到了嗎？", "name": "IANA"}}, {"id": 330, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "（聳肩）還差得遠。", "name": "TACHANKA"}}, {"id": 331, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "我想你們一定不介意多幾個旅伴幫你們一起找。", "name": "FUZE"}}, {"id": 332, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "哈哈哈，越多越好！", "name": "TACHANKA"}}, {"id": 333, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "呃，Lord，那個是……", "name": "DOC"}}, {"id": 334, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "各位，我來替Lord隆重介紹一下這款“烏薩斯特飲”——", "name": "BLITZ"}}, {"id": 335, "prop": "dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 336, "prop": "StopSound", "attributes": {"channel": "s", "fadetime": 2.0}}, {"id": 337, "prop": "StopSound", "attributes": {"channel": "c", "fadetime": 2.0}}, {"id": 338, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 1.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 1.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 339, "prop": "image", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 340, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "窗外忽然傳來吵鬧聲。"}}, {"id": 341, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "吃飽喝足的虹彩小隊成員們扭頭看去，習慣性地以為克里斯達爾藝術館外又出了什麼麻煩——"}}, {"id": 342, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "然後，第一個明白了是什麼情況的人無奈地聳了聳肩。"}}, {"id": 343, "prop": "dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 344, "prop": "Background", "attributes": {"image": "48_g4_galleriessquare_b", "screenadapt": "coverall"}}, {"id": 345, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_498_1#1$1"}}, {"id": 346, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 0.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "style": "slider", "inverse": "true", "fadetime": 2.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 347, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "我們已經跟老爹說好了，今天輪到我們跳沃爾珀小步舞的用這塊廣場，你們的古典音樂該關掉了！", "name": "社區畫家"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_498_1#1$1"}, {"id": 348, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_492_1#1$1"}}, {"id": 349, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "可是特克諾說她最近就喜歡聽我們三拍子的華爾滋！不信你問她，她就在牆旁邊！", "name": "窘迫的貴族"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_492_1#1$1"}, {"id": 350, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_022"}}, {"id": 351, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "就是就是！", "name": "社區居民"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_022"}, {"id": 352, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_498_1#1$1"}}, {"id": 353, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "特克諾，你過來，你說這事情到底怎麼辦？", "name": "社區畫家"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_498_1#1$1"}, {"id": 354, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_1212_1#8$1"}}, {"id": 355, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "哼，別用這種事煩我！", "name": "特克諾"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1212_1#8$1"}, {"id": 356, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_1212_1#1$1"}}, {"id": 357, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "有時間為了放什麼音樂吵架，不如來看看我的作品！", "name": "特克諾"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1212_1#1$1"}, {"id": 358, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_498_1#1$1"}}, {"id": 359, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "你的作品？可你的手……", "name": "社區畫家"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_498_1#1$1"}, {"id": 360, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_1212_1#9$1"}}, {"id": 361, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "哎呀，過來就知道了啦。", "name": "特克諾"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1212_1#9$1"}, {"id": 362, "prop": "CameraShake", "attributes": {"duration": 0.3, "xstrength": 30.0, "ystrength": 30.0, "vibrato": 30.0, "randomness": 90.0, "fadeout": "true", "block": "false"}}, {"id": 363, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_498_1#1$1"}}, {"id": 364, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "嗚哦！這……這真的是你畫的？", "name": "社區畫家"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_498_1#1$1"}, {"id": 365, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_1212_1#9$1"}}, {"id": 366, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "哈哈，我苦練了這麼長時間，終於抓到用左手發力的訣竅了！", "name": "特克諾"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1212_1#9$1"}, {"id": 367, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 368, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "特克諾，別練了，快進來！你一定沒喝過這種叫烏薩斯特飲的東西，再晚就沒有了哦！", "name": "迪亞茲"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1212_1#9$1"}, {"id": 369, "prop": "dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 370, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 0.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 0.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 371, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 1.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 3.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 372, "prop": "stopmusic", "attributes": {"fadetime": 2.0}}, {"id": 373, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 374, "prop": "Background", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 375, "prop": "Image", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 376, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": ""}}], "OPTIONTRACE": true}